{"tid":1430382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［忍唔住出po] 提防帶風撚 + 街頭心得","createTime":"2019-08-07T17:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:41:55.000Z","uid":169553,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2402af118328835afb851a6661fa422be8e9d25d","tid":1430382,"uid":169553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"代朋友出post，唔會回post<br />\n啱聽就聽唔啱聽冇所謂當聽人鳩up<br />\n<br />\n有幾句說話想同全部手足講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於帶風撚</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n連登係好撚多好撚多3毛，5毛<br />\n我諗好多手足都開post講過，往往成日好快沉咗落底。<br />\n<br />\n1.慣常<span style=\"font-size: large;\">半夜</span>由<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔同ac</span>開<span style=\"font-size: large;\">幾個post</span>，講<span style=\"font-size: large;\">同樣</span>話題，等你第二朝以爲好多人討論講左成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.post入面內容<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3分假7分真</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而且有唔同人係度<span style=\"color: red;\">互屌</span>，令你覺得好厭倦，你自然無咁投入場運動，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">高登當年都係咁死</span><br />\n<br />\n3.拉一派打一派，胡亂扣帽子<br />\n例子：我哋勇武派點點點，我地和理非點點點，可能有手足都會咁樣開post，但係五毛慣常都會<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有立場後扣帽子</span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令你覺得係果個立場既都要咁樣，影響你思路</span></span><br />\n例如：我係和理非都覺得你地過份左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n           就快選舉期下次見到議員，屌走佢，佢地就係選票/光環/曝光&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;民眾成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">關於街頭：</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.大家記得<span style=\"color: red;\">禮貌</span>好好<span style=\"font-size: large;\">拉攏中間嘅人</span>咁樣先至有得贏，唔好以為自己就係代表民意，因為真係有人活係平行世界。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如：見到人影相，唔好第一句就<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌佢老母！！！</span>同佢<span style=\"color: orange;\">好好解釋</span>點解唔可以影相，同埋自己都要包到成個愛斯基摩人咁，好好保護自己同身邊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最差情況佢要影佢都係影係你個愛斯基摩樣，佢影咗相唔肯del我都會好嬲，但我哋冇權力圍住佢，甚至搶佢手機，記住我地絕對同警犬唔同。當然如果佢郁手打人在先或者臥底警犬，你懂的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.前線真係會有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">鬼</span>（多數有喇叭）專登帶你遊花園，令到你<span style=\"color: orange;\">疲於奔命</span>，好似5/8金鐘&gt;銅鑼灣&gt;北角狗屋&gt;新光。時間容許嘅話可以<span style=\"font-size: large;\">禮貌問問佢點解</span>或者同其他手足討論下。好多時圍狗屋係聲援被捕者，無啦啦叫你去圍要停一停，諗一諗<br />\n太多情況講唔到，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時刻問自己為什麼好緊要。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3.你不合作運動一定有人屌你（塞地鐵室<br />\n塞稅局整路障），我地要明白果一刻確實係影響到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，先道歉後解釋話比佢聽點解二百萬人和平遊行，政府都唔回應，可以嘅話引到佢思考點解有不合作運動嘅出現。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">矛頭指向返政府</span></span>，真係唔得嘅道歉，令佢知道我哋都唔想。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">贏盡民意</span></span>。好似之前塞地鐵，<span style=\"color: orange;\">有手足建議塞40分鐘，放10分鐘，我覺得都係好好嘅做法。</span><br />\n<br />\n       <br />\n相信大家都係香港兒女聰明過人，一路以來我哋可以堅持咁耐，就係兄弟爬山各自努力，不割蓆。 手足做得唔好，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">可以屌，冷靜屌，慢慢屌，屌完，握手擁抱繼續頂硬上，千其唔好放棄任何一個人</span></span>，記著<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">成功四神獸</span></span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">和理非</span></span>+<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">deadline</span></span>+<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">民意</span></span>+<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">勇武</span></span>，要贏同同路人一定唔割！盡我地能力禮貌拉攏依然<br />\n不問世事既人！期望煲底除低口罩互相擁抱嘅日子！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nsorry for  1999"},{"pid":"25bf01b6bb1b4e963823527b71553e44edf3592a","tid":1430382,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"b5117b341a9d0cd02d9cc3201d89fe7b436c3ffb","tid":1430382,"uid":178630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33096bb8f46da55643e57f248d9f0cbb6cc0cdb","tid":1430382,"uid":169553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:38:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e36c07237da1fb208843ba441005d037eff0fae0","tid":1430382,"uid":260934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:38:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4292c520e345bf35e86c72c9a0800bc79303c5d","tid":1430382,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:44:22.000Z","msg":"手足你地小心比人動搖<br />\n例<br />\n淺藍或自稱淺黃既會話玩火 搞到宿舍過份左<br />\n玩黎有咩用 有人都開始動搖<br />\n<br />\n只要記住 各有各做 不割就可以<br />\n因為你想討好拉攏佢地，所以一齊指責前線既時候<br />\n 你已經係同勇武割左蓆"},{"pid":"6b39566c82f6c3baae807ed9994ef95f44040681","tid":1430382,"uid":129988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:52:33.000Z","msg":"借推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n浸大校長公然否定警察投訴機制！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1430356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1430356</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d236f1d23b63fa7b9343948e935686a9f9b7627","tid":1430382,"uid":169553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2402af118328835afb851a6661fa422be8e9d25d","tid":1430382,"uid":169553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"代朋友出post，唔會回post<br />\n啱聽就聽唔啱聽冇所謂當聽人鳩up<br />\n<br />\n有幾句說話想同全